</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="54.[151,1436,828,1213]" box="[199,926,1116,1141]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,323,1116,1141]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">Bionomics</emphasis>
. Adults fly in February. Otherwise biology unknown.
</paragraph>
